race.comment: RATTLIN' BONES (1) showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten 1.75 lengths over 300m this track in 16.68. Can measure up this time. GOT FLAIR (3) was out of the placings last time when sixth at this track (19.89) but scored five back at this track (19.37). Has a good record here at this journey. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to run well. SIMPLY STYLISH (7) missed the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 390m at Shepparton in 22.08. Top win two back and rates a key player again. ROOM TO BREATHE (5) has definite claims at his first try at this journey.
